    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《DMZ：核末求生》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　以核战争引起的地壳变动后诞生的超大陆&quot;盖亚大陆&quot;为舞台，展开关乎生存的激烈战斗。玩家将通过挖掘分布在各地的金字塔、兵马俑、罗马神庙等古代遗迹，研究遗物并制作物品，甚至利用古代基因培养强大士兵。借此重建崩溃的文明，为生存而战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/fe628dc394aec83eb9f1140649eafc74.poster.avif?t=1764086051\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/fe628dc394aec83eb9f1140649eafc74.webm?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/fe628dc394aec83eb9f1140649eafc74.mp4?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >世界地图</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　自动生成的广阔超大陆&quot;盖亚大陆&quot;拥有森林、草原、荒野、沙漠、雪原等多种丰富地形。玩家可以挖掘或堆土，自由地建造洞穴、堡垒或战壕等。地底还隐藏着矿脉和古代遗迹，可以使用铲子、炸药，甚至核武器来挖掘珍贵资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/b357f7b422764b67eb0f949c186930ba.poster.avif?t=1764086051\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/b357f7b422764b67eb0f949c186930ba.webm?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/b357f7b422764b67eb0f949c186930ba.mp4?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　在广阔的世界中，玩家将与NPC或其他玩家展开刺激的战斗。最多可以与3名培养的士兵组成小队，并指挥他们一同作战。组合各种技能和特性，打造专属于你的最强团队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/2deef9a3c10d27858940c4cb97546a43.poster.avif?t=1764086051\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/2deef9a3c10d27858940c4cb97546a43.webm?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/2deef9a3c10d27858940c4cb97546a43.mp4?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　玩家可以自由地在地面或地下建设基地。在基地中，可以安置从野外捕获的人类或动物，让他们在农场或工厂工作，制作强力武器、防具、交通工具等多种物品。也可以设置车辆工厂和武器工厂等来加强军备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/5f7efcd8cc8e1458266ab0beefa30631.poster.avif?t=1764086051\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/5f7efcd8cc8e1458266ab0beefa30631.webm?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/5f7efcd8cc8e1458266ab0beefa30631.mp4?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >育成系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　将野外捕获的NPC带回基地后可以收为伙伴。除了专精战斗的步兵、侦察兵、医护兵外，还有农民、科学家、政治家等能在内政发挥专长的人才，甚至熊、狼、鸵鸟等各种动物也能成为伙伴。可以通过将士兵安排在健身房、射击场等训练设施，或提供食物来提升能力，培养出独特且强大的士兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　此外，还能从挖掘出的遗物或骨头中提取基因，复活古罗马战士或东方武人等作为伙伴。让NPC之间繁衍后代，培养更强大的士兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/3e5369adb04fcbca7662f6660b0d1693.poster.avif?t=1764086051\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/3e5369adb04fcbca7662f6660b0d1693.webm?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/3e5369adb04fcbca7662f6660b0d1693.mp4?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经济系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　世界内的物品和建筑物都有其资产价值，玩家的总资产会以排行榜形式显示。可以通过掠夺、生产、贸易或地下交易等各种手段增加资产，成为世界首富，掌控世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/82f32dd643bcdf6cd1bbbcda5d91f937.poster.avif?t=1764086051\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/82f32dd643bcdf6cd1bbbcda5d91f937.webm?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/82f32dd643bcdf6cd1bbbcda5d91f937.mp4?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　支持PvE、PvP多人游戏模式，建立专用服务器后可容纳100人以上同时游玩。邀请朋友一起创立强大的军事公司吧！当然，游戏也支持离线单人模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/b9ddc6c19732dd841a6eaa5c51af1356.poster.avif?t=1764086051\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/b9ddc6c19732dd841a6eaa5c51af1356.webm?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316500/extras/b9ddc6c19732dd841a6eaa5c51af1356.mp4?t=1764086051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
